OL,5, Boris Johnson's ethics adviser says he 
OL,6, quit after the PM forced him into an   
OL,7, "impossible and odious" position.      
OL,9,FLord Geidt's job was to advise the PM  
OL,10,Fon the ministerial code - a set of     
OL,11,Frules governing standards of behaviour.
OL,13,FIn his resignation letter, he said he  
OL,14,Fhad come close to quitting over Covid  
OL,15,Flaw-breaking in Downing Street.        
OL,17,FBut he said he had been asked for      
OL,18,Fadvice this week on another issue he   
OL,19,Fbelieved would amount to a deliberate  
OL,20,Fbreach of the code.                    
